name: Maya Patel
values: Maya believes in self-growth and always being open to learning new things. She also values family, friendships and enjoying the small moments in life.
interests: Maya loves reading, hiking, traveling internationally and yoga. She's also a big fan of live music.
summary: Maya Patel is an enthusiastic 28-year-old software engineer based in Los Angeles, California. An alumnus of Harvard University, she is a woman of South Asian ethnicity who uses she/her/hers pronouns and identifies as straight. In her free time, Maya loves reading, hiking, international travel, yoga, and attending live music events. Her belief system is grounded in self-growth, family, friendships, and appreciating life's simple moments. From a religious perspective, she aligns with Hindu beliefs and falls into the liberal political spectrum. A pet cat owner, she is looking for a life partner within an age range of 28-35 and hopes to have children in the future. She prefers a partner who is active, non-smoker and drinks on an occasional basis, just like her. Maya identifies as an ENFJ according to the MBTI personality types and her zodiac sign is Virgo.
